quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,9,"And had We appointed him an angel, We indeed would have made him a man, and We would have certainly confused them in which they are already confused (i.e. the Message of Prophet Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم)."
  6,10,"And indeed (many) Messengers before you were mocked at, but their scoffers were surrounded by the very thing that they used to mock at."